name: Flow State
description: Beneath the chatty subconscious lies a state of flow - a calm amongst the chaos. My mind is grounded by repetition, rhythm, patterns and frequencies. This flow state is solitary and fragile, existing beneath the layers of myself. It is a mirror of my environment, often navigating a line between order and disorder. It speaks to a desire to be alone but also the need to coexist. Sound design by 500 Mills.
